<paragraph blockId="7.[136,1452,158,472]" pageId="7" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,435,158,184]" pageId="7" pageNumber="183">Conservation status:</emphasis>
—This species is here assessed as endangered, EN B1ab(i) + 2ab(i) (
<bibRefCitation author="IUCN" box="[1191,1327,158,184]" pageId="7" pageNumber="183" refId="ref13533" refString="IUCN (2001) IUCN Red list categories and criteria: version 3.1. IUCN Species Survival Commission, Gland, 30 pp." type="book" year="2001">IUCN 2001</bibRefCitation>
